name: 甘奈
text: ……あーっ、ダメ！　プロデューサーさん！
trans: ...Ah— This isn't great at all! Producer-san!

name: 甘奈
text: やっぱり緊張する、今までで一番ドキドキしてる……！
trans:
I'm getting really nervous! I think this is the most
nerve-wracking moment I've had today...!

name: プロデューサー
text:
！？
じゃあ緊張が解けるように、何か──
trans:
!? Then, maybe there's a way to help you shake off
that nervousness—

name: 甘奈
text: うん、だから、お願いしてもいい……！？
trans: Yeah... Could I ask you for something then...!?

name: 甘奈
text:
甘奈のこと、応援して
頑張ってこいって言って
trans:
Please support me like this: Tell me to do my best out
there.

name: 甘奈
text: 甘奈ならできるって言って
trans:
And also tell me that if anyone can do it, it's me, and
that I can do it.

name: プロデューサー
text:
大丈夫。甘奈ならできるよ
だから、頑張ってこい
trans:
It's alright, Amana. This is you we're talking about
 You can do this. So go out there and give it your very
best!
